These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, march, november, june
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, drama, superhero
There 4 different types of food: spinach, cherry, mango, papaya
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, goat, goldfish
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, reading, drawing, photography
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person eating papaya is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's hobby is photography##2
 3. the owner of the cat is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person eating mango##2
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Birthday           | november | december   | june | march |
| Movie-Genre   | crime      | disaster | drama              | superhero |
| Food   | spinach       | cherry     | papaya               | mango    |
| Pet           | dog        | goat     | goldfish           | cat       |
| Hobby     | reading | drawing     | puzzles                | photography      |

