.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, begonia, iris, bellflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, police-officer, project-manager
4 different games are played: chess, whist, go, billiard
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, lavender, ebony, coral
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the police-officer is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 2. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 3. the freelancer is between the person who growsiris and the person who likes lavender##2
 4. the person playing billiard is the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the person who likes ebony is the freelancer##1
 6. the police-officer is on the left of the electrician##1
 7. the project-manager is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the police-officer##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the electrician##1
10. the police-officer is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the person who growsiris##1
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Flower          | iris       | begonia      | balloon-flower      | bellflower      |
| Job           | project-manager | freelancer | police-officer | electrician |
| Game   | billiard          | whist       | go            | chess      |
| Color           | yellow            | ebony    | lavender           | coral       |
| Sport         | handball        | sailing    | tennis         | volleyball  |

