4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, horse, mouse
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, lily, daisy, amaryllis
 1. the british is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the japanese##1
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who growslily##1
 5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 6. the person who likes light-blue is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who growsbellflower##2
 7. the british is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 8. the person who likes azure is the person who growsdaisy##1
 9. the british is the owner of the mouse##1
10. the colombian is on the far left##1
11. the colombian is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
