.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, video-games, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, romance, time-travel, drama
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, house, jazz, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, parkour, snowboarding, soccer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, bolivar, havana, dunhill
 1. the havana-smoker is the person watching thriller movies##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is between the fan of disco and the fan of house##2
 3. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the fan of house is between the person who's sport is cricket and the old-henry-smoker##2
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is the dunhill-smoker##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the bolivar-smoker and the fan of jazz##2
10. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
11. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Hobby      | filmmaking     | puzzles | video-games    | collecting          |
| Movie-Genre          | drama | thriller     | time-travel | romance         |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | house       | pop         | disco        |
| Sport         | soccer  | parkour     | cricket     | snowboarding |
| Cigar     | old-henry     | havana      | bolivar   | dunhill          |

