4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, fonseca, davidoff, blend
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, mexican, spanish
 1. the blend-smoker is the person who likes red##1
 2. the blend-smoker is on the left of the german##1
 3. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 5. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
 6. the spanish is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 7. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person eating corn is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
10. the person who likes red is between the person who likes blood-red and the person drinking 7up##2
11. the canadian is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
12. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |      4       |
| Food          | asparagus    | corn        | cranberry    | watermelon   |
| Color         | ebony | red | blood-red    | orange      |
| Beverage           | 7up       | coffee   | mirinda        | lemonade |
