 6. the fan of indie is the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
11. the person who likes ivory is between the person traveling to new-york and the person driving the taxi##2
12. the person who likes lilac is between the person driving the roller and the person playing monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Game      | domino      | monopoly         | snooker | poker      |
| City           | new-york | rome | prague | san-francisco     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa         | indie          | ambient  | electronic |
| Color         | turquise        | ivory  | lilac | pink   |
| Transport     | skateboard    | subway         | taxi     | roller     |

