 7. the person who growslily is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 8. the fan of gospel is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 9. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is the swisher-smoker##1
11. the swisher-smoker is the person who's sport is sailing##1

